---
title: Stir-Fried Five-Spice Chili Beef with Green Peppers and Mushrooms
description: The trick with this dish is to cook the beef in a super hot frying pan in batches. By leaving space between each ribbon in the pan, they’ll crisp up rather than stew. Let us know how it goes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/stir-fried-five-spice-chili-beef-a6d374a4.jpg
